BSC-BPM
===================================================================
Warning! BSC-BPM is not stable. Check the releases page for the latest stable versions.


Update: 3.2.1
===================================================================
In the most recent update, I added a man page, more make commands, 
commands that aren't install or remove now have two dashes. (e.g. 'bpm update-log' is now 'bpm --update-log'), 
and you can now update (kind of) bpm, with the command 'bpm --update.' [Bug fix] Command failures and successes now return
correct integer. I have also added a license.

man page: 'man bpm'


Upcoming Features
===================================================================
MHS-FS Filesystem support

────────────────────────────────────┐
Compiling, Installing, and Updating.│
────────────────────────────────────┘

Installation
===================================================================
git clone https://github.com/BizzyPythonBear/BearShellC-BPM BSC-BPM
cd BSC-BPM
sudo make install
bpm --help

Updating
===================================================================
sudo make update

Compiling (If you decided to make your own changes to the code)
===================================================================
sudo make compile
